cs.PL, cs.OS, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.SY

The paper discusses the design and implementation of a record-and-replay system, which involves programming languages (cs.PL), operating systems (cs.OS), and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the need for certain hardware and operating system constraints (cs.SY) to support their approach. Additionally, the paper discusses optimizations for real-world workloads (cs.AR).
